                    </li>
                    <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                      <span class="text-cyan-500 font-bold">•</span>
                      <span><strong>Drywall:</strong> Cut and remove at least 12 inches above the waterline</span>
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                      <span class="text-cyan-500 font-bold">•</span>
                      <span><strong>Insulation:</strong> If wet, it won't dry and will grow mold — remove it</span>
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                      <span class="text-cyan-500 font-bold">•</span>
                      <span><strong>Baseboards and trim:</strong> Usually warped beyond repair — remove to dry wall cavity</span>
                    </li>
                  </ul>
